quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  55,1,"The Merciful One"
  55,2,"has taught the Qur'an,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  55,3,"has created man,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  55,4,"and has taught him articulate speech."{1},footnotes:1:1
  55,5,"The sun and the moon follow a reckoning,"{1},footnotes:1:1
  55,6,"and the stars and the trees all prostrate themselves,"{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  55,7,"and He has raised up the heaven and has set a balance"{1},footnotes:1:1
  55,8,"that you may not transgress in the balance,"
  55,9,"but weigh things equitably and skimp not in the balance."{1},footnotes:1:1
  55,10,"And He has set up the earth for all beings."{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2